**/TOKEN_SECRET*

# AWS-specific sensitive files
**/api-gateway-url.*
**/lambda-config.*
**/aws-config.*
**/api-url.*
**/gateway-url.*

# Subscriber data (may contain real email addresses and personal data)
**/subscribers.json
**/subscribers.*.json
**/subscribers-backup.*

# Production configuration files
**/config.prod.*
**/production.*
**/*.prod.*

# Environment variables (may contain secrets)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.env

